  EncounterId: H1_COFFEE
  Type: 0
  QuestionTextAR: "\u062A\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0627\u0634\u0631\u0628 \u0642\u0647\u0648\u0629
    \u064A\u0627 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u064A"
  Choices:
  - TextAR: "\u0644\u0627 \u0634\u0643\u0631\u0627\u064B"
    BatteryDelta: -0.2
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 2
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: Saying 'no thank you' verbally is often ignored. You must shake
      the finjan cup to signal you are done.
  - TextAR: "\u0634\u0643\u0631\u0627\u064B \u062E\u0627\u0644\u062A\u064A \u0643\u062B\u064A\u0631
      \u0627\u0633\u062A\u0641\u062F\u062A"
    BatteryDelta: 0.1
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 4
    IsCorrect: 1
    FeedbackText: Accepting graciously while signalling fullness respects both the
      host and the tradition.
  - TextAR: "\u0645\u0627 \u0628\u062F\u064A"
    BatteryDelta: -0.3
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 1
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: "Blunt refusal is considered \u0631\u0641\u0636 \u0648\u0642\u062D
      \u2014 rude rejection. The host's generosity must always be honoured gently."
  PanicTimerDuration: 8
  TriggersMiniGame: 0
